{"lastModified":1771849580262,"uri":"c::8345304695::vessel::d5cbfb54-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nLagoon 450 F Luxury “Bright Moon” combines plenty of relaxing outdoor spaces with a stylish interior. In addition, she is offering stability at anchor, tremendous visibility and excellent sailing performances. The saloon flows easily into the cockpit. All the space is bright and open, so you hardly notice whether you are inside or outside. But it’s the open-air spaces that shine on this boat so make sure you reserve one of the big lockers for a couple of gallons of sunscreen. The natural light and ample storage space offer additional comfort.\n\nCruising under sail has its own special allure. Guests can be assured of a superb charter experience. “Bright Moon” has all of the services and equipment you need to enjoy an endless variety of fun and relaxing activities during your sailing vacation. There are four double cabins, all air-conditioned and with private bathrooms. “Bright Moon” is a luxury version that has the highest technology solutions. She is a fantastic choice for families or groups. Relax and enjoy soaking up the sunshine on her trampolines! Furthermore, numerous water toys and additional entertainment contents are provided for your pleasure.\n\nSailing in Croatia is at the top of every holiday and bucket list so Book your sailing vacation fast and enjoy your holidays.","blueprint":{"name":"BRIGHT MOON","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb54-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::0bc011d0-bca4-11ef-8098-87e747d2c5de/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb54-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::0bd03e70-bca4-11ef-8098-87e747d2c5de/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb54-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::0ba38920-bca4-11ef-8098-87e747d2c5de/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb54-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::0bb